# PA Media Booking — live deploy

Deploy to **pamedia.art** with SFTP only. Do **not** use wp-admin Plugin Editor, CDP `Runtime.evaluate`, or browser console deploy loops.

## Credentials

- Config: `~/Desktop/Cursor Projects/.env.sftp` (gitignored)
- Password: macOS Keychain service `pa-media-booking-sftp`
- First-time setup (user runs locally): `bash pa-media-booking/bin/setup-sftp-credentials.sh`

## Deploy command

From `~/Desktop/Cursor Projects/`:

```bash
bash deploy-sftp.sh
```

Then remind user to **Flush Cache** in wp-admin (GoDaddy Quick Links) if CSS/JS changed.

## Remote paths

- Plugin: `/html/wp-content/plugins/pa-media-booking.disabled`
- MU plugin: `/html/wp-content/mu-plugins/pa-booking-godaddy-paylink.php`
